@startuml

title Information flow — upward (signal)

skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor #2A2A2E
    BorderColor #58A6FF
    FontColor #E3E3E6
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #1A1A1E
    BorderColor #58A6FF
    FontColor #E3E3E6
}
skinparam ArrowColor #8AB4F8
skinparam ArrowFontColor #E3E3E6
skinparam BackgroundColor transparent
skinparam DefaultFontColor #E3E3E6

rectangle "Task completion\n(S1)"          as Task
rectangle "Story completion\n(S2)"         as Story
rectangle "Sprint retrospective\n(S3)"     as Sprint
rectangle "Version release notes\n(S4)"    as Version
rectangle "Identity check\n(S5)"           as Identity

Task     --> Story    : surfaces
Story    --> Sprint   : surfaces
Sprint   --> Version  : surfaces
Version  --> Identity : surfaces

note right of Task
  Each lower level
  surfaces what
  actually happened
  to the level above.
end note

@enduml
